2006-08-04  Vincent Geddes <vincent.geddes@gmail.com>

	* doc/catalogintro.sgml, doc/children.sgml, doc/gladeui-docs.sgml,
	  doc/tmpl/glade-app.sgml, doc/tmpl/glade-fixed.sgml,
